column5: Heading to Whitefish Bay Camp in 2 weeks, we've never been to this part of LOTW before so any tips on the area would be appreciated. We pretty much only fish for pike but since we've never been there the main thing will be to catch something to build up some confidence so any info would be appreciated.
You might check out the web site for Witch Bay Camp, they usually share a fairly extensive fishing report.http://www.witchbay.com/fishrpt.htm Bill Krejca Krejca
